%h2.page-title
	Grid -
	%span.fw-semi-bold Live
	%small Draggable widgets. Touch screen support
.row
	.col-md-7.col-lg-offset-1
		%section.widget
			%header
				%h4
					New Widgets &nbsp;
					%span.label.label-danger since 2.1
			.body
				%p
					Specially for Light Blue 2.1 we have developed a plugin that allows to easily implement basic widget functions that
					lots of our customers have requested. The plugin is called
					= succeed "." do
						%strong Widgster
					For now it has the following essential
					widget features:
				%ul.text-list
					%li
						%strong Collapse/Expand
						\- all widgets can be collapsed to fill only header's vertical space;
					%li
						%strong Close
						\- closable. Any widget may be removed by clicking the close btn;
					%li
						%strong Full Screen
						\- an option to make widget fill the whole window (just like OS);
					%li
						%strong Ajax Load
						\- the hottest option allowing to load/reload widget content asynchronously. You just
						need to provide an url to fetch the data from. With loader delivered.
				%p In the future this plugin may be released under MIT license, but for now it's available exclusively with Light Blue.
				%p
					Test it out!
